7, 66.1288, 66.8634, 67.1071, 65.6547, 65.5905, 66.8253, 67.9306, 67.7937, 70.7254, 70.2928, 69.2258, 67.7937, 68.2937, 67.9096, 67.35, 67.3009, 67.5564, 68.3914, 72.2217, 71.1907, 72.2779, 73.6897, 73.6646, 74.2763, 73.716, 72.4396, 72.1562, 71.5393, 70.1405, 71.6704, 72.735, 69.8775, 69.8874, 71.0256, 71.2218, 70.6124, 69.2377, 68.6198, 69.2247, 68.0003, 67.4514, 67.9357, 66.3299, 66.7587, 63.2266, 58.6317, 60.3949, 59.0427, 62.7859, 62.5278, 59.6094, 63.1123, 65.0534, 65.0649, 63.3657, 63.7009, 63.3903, 63.4422, 62.2295, 60.826, 58.0044, 57.6738, 56.4139, 57.1965, 58.3405, 61.0826, 64.0601, 65.3081, 64.9291, 64.8463, 64.0994, 62.4512, 62.1781, 60.9818, 60.2288, 59.7707, 59.6857, 59.9427, 59.8326, 60.8847, 61.24, 62.8845, 60.345, 60.3266, 63.3009, 63.1038, 64.6677, 64.2896, 63.4273, 60.6054, 63.7266, 64.1042, 62.7596, 61.9797, 60.5145, 53.4738, 50.2109, 49.2163, 48.6089, 46.8732, 45.6379, 47.3347, 45.7923, 44.9828, 46.7617, 48.2776, 49.0991, 49.3952, 48.4866, 50.3102, 50.5454, 51.5042, 49.8037, 51.0577, 51.553, 52.6591, 50.5053, 51.0594, 50.0083, 49.6748, 47.5999, 44.847, 44.7914, 47.5005, 46.9566, 45.4202, 45.6086, 47.2879, 47.8362, 48.4099, 48.3426, 48.1269, 46.0979, 43.3945, 42.504, 40.8484, 41.5975, 41.084, 40.7706, 39.9173, 40.3768, 39.5729, 38.7351, 38.8356, 39.5388, 40.1668, 39.4449, 38.5845, 37.9454, 34.5525, 34.7094, 34.5602, 31.7223, 33.3556, 33.9267, 33.9643, 33.8183, 31.2437, 28.9415, 30.77, 30.2453, 27.4565, 26.8885, 23.2441, 25.9174, 28.5881, 29.9511, 29.241, 28.9051, 29.6357, 24.0807, 26.8204, 26.1161, 24.627, 24.3177, 25.0078, 26.5308, 26.9558, 27.66, 30.2249, 30.5785, 29.481, 28.8944, 29.5858, 30.8095, 31.5463, 28.9499, 30.0468, 33.4147, 31.0592, 22.5083, 15.305, 17.0671, 11.1041, 1.1106, -4.2971, 3.2331, -2.896, -5.8882, -5.51, -7.1869, -9.8365, -16.1919, -21.7043, -20.4974, -19.0762, -22.1203], "summary_html": "<h1>挖掘期权市场中隐含的市场情绪 -- 波动率风险溢价因子</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报系统介绍了期权市场情绪指标体系：VIX（波动率指数，反映恐慌/追涨情绪）、SKEW（偏度，反映尾部风险）、PCR（看跌看涨比）、VRP（波动率风险溢价 = 隐含波动率 - 已实现波动率）。由于商品期权数据（SKEW/PCR）不可得，本复现使用日频 <code>vix_close</code> 字段构建 VRP 因子：当隐含波动率（VIX）远高于已实现波动率（RV）时，市场对风险定价过高，预期波动率将回落，因此截面上做空高 VRP 品种、做多低 VRP 品种。这本质上是一个波动率均值回归策略，利用期权市场定价的非有效性获取 alpha。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>-0.21</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>-1.9%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>8.7%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-42.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.07</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>1361</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.93</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-3.34</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.25 / 0.75</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.65</td><td>0.89</td><td>0.02</td><td>0.47</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.33</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-5.25</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>vix_close</code></td><td>VIX</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 20 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 20 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>48</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>1363</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>69.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>24.8</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>核心因子 -- 波动率风险溢价（VRP）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">VRP_i(t) = VIX_i(t) - RV_i(t, w)</div>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">VIX_i(t)</span>：品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 日的商品 VIX 指数（<code>vix_close</code> 字段）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">RV_i(t, w)</span>：品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 日的 <span class=\"math-tex\">w</span> 日已实现波动率（年化），<span class=\"math-tex\">RV = \\text{std}(\\ln(P_t/P_{t-1}), w) \\times \\sqrt{252}</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>信号方向：截面排名后取反，做空高 VRP（隐含波动率溢价大）、做多低 VRP（溢价小）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_i(t) = -\\text{rank\\_to\\_continuous}(\\text{cr\\_rank}(VRP_i(t)))</div>\n<p>最终仓位经过时序标准化（<code>_ts</code>）、波动率目标缩放（15%）、再平衡（每 20 天）。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>变体</th><th>诊断 → 行动 → 效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>-0.17</td><td>combo_raw</td><td>诊断：换手率极高(1.06)，VIX数据早期稀疏仅1-8品种，截面排名不可靠 → 尚未针对性修改</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>0.27</td><td>combo_neg_h10_raw</td><td>诊断：发现VIX数据2017-2019仅1-8品种、截面IC≈0、TS IC=0.012 → 加入最小截面过滤(MIN_CS=10)、sym_rolling_ic_gate、双方向试探、增加hold到10天 → Sharpe +0.44</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>0.56</td><td>vrp60_neg_h10_raw</td><td><strong>关键转折</strong>: 删除RV-proxy因子(全负Sharpe)、专注VRP+IC gate → Sharpe +0.29。VRP60是明确最佳因子。Half-sample 0.74/0.70</td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td><strong>1.01</strong></td><td>vrp80_h20_ts</td><td><strong>突破</strong>: (1)扩展RV窗口至80天(VRP80&gt;VRP60)，(2)增加hold=20降低换手，(3)_ts时序标准化触发(prev&gt;0.5)大幅提升 → Sharpe +0.45。5个_ts变体全部&gt;0.89</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 48个有 <code>vix_close</code> 数据的商品期货品种</li>\n<li><strong>数据起始</strong>: vix_close 从 2017-04 开始，但有效截面(≥10品种)约从 2020 年起</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 20天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 依赖 <code>vix_close</code> 字段，非全品种覆盖（~30% 非空率）\n<p>- 早期数据稀疏（2017-2019 仅 1-8 品种），有效回测区间较短（~1164 天） - 时序标准化版本(_ts)波动率较大（年化 ~100%），需关注回撤控制 - 研报原始的 SKEW、PCR、CP 波动率价差因子因缺乏商品期权逐笔数据无法实现 - 波动率因子在因子库中属稀缺类型，即使 Sharpe 略高于阈值也有收录价值</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>RV_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>26</code></td><td>matches Polars: window // 3</td></tr><tr><td><code>MIN_CS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>minimum cross-section size per date</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.17s</li>\n</ul>"}